[
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=3"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hello, and welcome to \"Meet In-App Events ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the App Store.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=11"
  },
  {
    "text": "My name is Will Averill, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "and I'm an engineering manager on the App Store Connect team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=13"
  },
  {
    "text": "The App Store is more than a store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=17"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a daily destination designed to help users discover ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=19"
  },
  {
    "text": "all the rich experiences that apps have to offer. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "So they can find their next favorite app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "or get the most out of the ones they already have. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=27"
  },
  {
    "text": "This fall, we're taking this even further with In-App Events. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "In-App Events are timely events within your apps and games, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "such as a game competition, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "a fitness challenge, a movie premiere, and more. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=40"
  },
  {
    "text": "In fact, some of you may already be ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "running events inside your apps. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=46"
  },
  {
    "text": "For those of you who aren't, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=47"
  },
  {
    "text": "now is a great time to consider doing so. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=49"
  },
  {
    "text": "That's because this fall, In-App Events will be ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "discoverable right on the App Store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "This a whole new way to showcase your app's events ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "and expand their reach. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=59"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this session, I'll show you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=61"
  },
  {
    "text": "how In-App Events work on the App Store ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how to create them in App Store Connect.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "In-App Events appear on the App Store ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=68"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the new event card. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=70"
  },
  {
    "text": "The design is focused on letting your content come ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "front and center and supports either an image or a video. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=75"
  },
  {
    "text": "The event card also displays your event name, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=79"
  },
  {
    "text": "a short description, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "and a time indicator, which automatically updates ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "as the event approaches and once it starts. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=85"
  },
  {
    "text": "Users who have your app installed will be able ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "to jump right into the event by tapping Open. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=90"
  },
  {
    "text": "This event card is discoverable across the App Store, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=93"
  },
  {
    "text": "beginning with your product page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here, on your app's product page, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=98"
  },
  {
    "text": "events are listed in order of their start and priority. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "Their location on the product page varies, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "with events appearing above screenshots ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=107"
  },
  {
    "text": "for users who have downloaded your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=109"
  },
  {
    "text": "and below screenshots for those who haven't. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tapping the event card brings up the event details page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=114"
  },
  {
    "text": "The event details page, with its longer description ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "and larger media asset, gives users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=120"
  },
  {
    "text": "additional context around your event. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=122"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also link directly to your event details page ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=125"
  },
  {
    "text": "by appending the unique event ID to your app's App Store URL.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=127"
  },
  {
    "text": "In order to build anticipation for events, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=133"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'll be able to promote them ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=135"
  },
  {
    "text": "up to two weeks before they start. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "And users will be able to easily request ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=138"
  },
  {
    "text": "a notification for when your event begins. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=140"
  },
  {
    "text": "These notifications come from the App Store ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=143"
  },
  {
    "text": "and will launch users directly into the event inside your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=146"
  },
  {
    "text": "If the user doesn't have your app installed, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=149"
  },
  {
    "text": "they will be directed to the event details page.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=151"
  },
  {
    "text": "In-App Events are also discoverable through search. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=155"
  },
  {
    "text": "Users who search for your app will see the event card ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "along with the app if they've downloaded it before. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "For those users who haven't downloaded your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "they will instead see screenshots alongside your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "When users search directly for your In-App Event, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=169"
  },
  {
    "text": "the event card always appears next to your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "On the Games and Apps tabs, users will see personalized ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "event recommendations that can help them stay informed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "about the apps and games they already have, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=181"
  },
  {
    "text": "find something new, or rediscover an old favorite. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "And lastly, our editorial team will be ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "curating the most exciting and innovative events ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=190"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the Today, Games, and Apps tabs. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=192"
  },
  {
    "text": "In-App Events will be available on iOS and iPadOS. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that you've seen what In-App Events look like ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the App Store, let me show you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=202"
  },
  {
    "text": "how to create an event in App Store Connect.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=204"
  },
  {
    "text": "Start by logging in and navigating ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=208"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the app you wanna create an event for. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=210"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then click the new In-App Events option ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "under Features on the left. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "This takes you to a high-level overview of your app's events. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=219"
  },
  {
    "text": "Since you're creating your first event, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=223"
  },
  {
    "text": "there's not much here at the moment. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "So click the \"Create In-App Event\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=227"
  },
  {
    "text": "to begin the process.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "You're then asked to provide a Reference Name ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=232"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your new event. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=234"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your event's reference name is only visible ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=236"
  },
  {
    "text": "within App Store Connect. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "Pick a reference name up to 64 characters long ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "and click Create. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=244"
  },
  {
    "text": "With your event now created, you land on the event page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=246"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here, you'll provide all the information necessary ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "to publish your In-App Event to the App Store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=251"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll start by filling in some of the most fundamental metadata ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=254"
  },
  {
    "text": "about your event under the Event Information section. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=257"
  },
  {
    "text": "All fields under Event Information are localized. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=261"
  },
  {
    "text": "Click the current language for a drop-down ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=265"
  },
  {
    "text": "of all available localizations. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=267"
  },
  {
    "text": "You should consider broadening your event's audience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=269"
  },
  {
    "text": "by localizing for as many languages as possible. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=272"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you've selected your intended language, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'll need to pick an event name. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=278"
  },
  {
    "text": "This name has a limit of 30 characters ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "and will appear throughout the App Store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll also point out that as you fill in ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=286"
  },
  {
    "text": "the fields on the left, those values are rendered ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=287"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the preview window on the right. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=290"
  },
  {
    "text": "The preview window shows both the event card ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=292"
  },
  {
    "text": "and event details page as they will appear on the App Store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=295"
  },
  {
    "text": "From looking at the preview window, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can see that the event name is shown on both.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=300"
  },
  {
    "text": "The short description is used on the event card and is used ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=304"
  },
  {
    "text": "to briefly summarize your event with up to 50 characters.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=308"
  },
  {
    "text": "As the name suggests, the event card media ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "is the image or video that appears on your event card. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": "While the long description ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=319"
  },
  {
    "text": "is used on the event details page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "This has a 120-character limit, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=323"
  },
  {
    "text": "so you can include additional details, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "like potential rewards, for example.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=327"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, you'll add either an image or video ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=330"
  },
  {
    "text": "for the event details page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=333"
  },
  {
    "text": "Videos you use on both the card and details page ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=335"
  },
  {
    "text": "will loop and are limited to 30 seconds.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=338"
  },
  {
    "text": "Lastly, pick from the badge options ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=342"
  },
  {
    "text": "to define the type of event you're running. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=344"
  },
  {
    "text": "This badge is displayed on the card ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "and details views on the App Store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=348"
  },
  {
    "text": "With your Event Information now finished, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=352"
  },
  {
    "text": "let's continue down the page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=354"
  },
  {
    "text": "Just like Apps and In-App Purchases, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'll need to define availability ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=359"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your In-App Event on a per Country ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=361"
  },
  {
    "text": "or Region basis. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=363"
  },
  {
    "text": "Click the Edit button to open the Country and Region selector, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=365"
  },
  {
    "text": "something that should be familiar to most of you. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=369"
  },
  {
    "text": "The only difference here ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=373"
  },
  {
    "text": "is that your In-App Event can only be made available ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=374"
  },
  {
    "text": "in Countries where your parent app is available. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=376"
  },
  {
    "text": "After deciding availability, you need to schedule your event, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=380"
  },
  {
    "text": "which means defining its start, end, and publish date and times.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "Event start represents when your event begins ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=389"
  },
  {
    "text": "inside your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=391"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll also need to define when the event ends inside your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=394"
  },
  {
    "text": "Together, the start and end represent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=398"
  },
  {
    "text": "the total duration of your In-App Event. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=400"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your event can run as long as 31 days ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=403"
  },
  {
    "text": "or as short as 15 minutes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=405"
  },
  {
    "text": "The next thing you'll need to consider is when you want ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=408"
  },
  {
    "text": "your event to first appear on the App Store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is controlled by your event's publish date, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=414"
  },
  {
    "text": "which can be up to 14 days from your event's start.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=416"
  },
  {
    "text": "When your event is published to the App Store, it will be ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=421"
  },
  {
    "text": "discoverable through all of the ways we discussed earlier, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=423"
  },
  {
    "text": "like on your product page and in search. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=426"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once your event reaches its end, it is no longer discoverable ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the App Store by browsing or searching.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=432"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, users will still be able to see ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=436"
  },
  {
    "text": "your event details page ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=439"
  },
  {
    "text": "via the App Store URL for another 30 days, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=440"
  },
  {
    "text": "after which point, it is then archived. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=443"
  },
  {
    "text": "This ensures links you've shared through marketing channels ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=446"
  },
  {
    "text": "will still work for a while after the event ends. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=449"
  },
  {
    "text": "This 30-day period happens automatically ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=452"
  },
  {
    "text": "and is not configurable. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=454"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you want to archive your In-App Event sooner, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=456"
  },
  {
    "text": "you're able to do so by editing its availability ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=459"
  },
  {
    "text": "in App Store Connect.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=461"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that you've set up your event's default scheduling, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=464"
  },
  {
    "text": "you're given the ability to set custom scheduling ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=467"
  },
  {
    "text": "per Country or Region. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=469"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is completely optional, but to do so, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=471"
  },
  {
    "text": "click the \"Customize Dates and Times\" link. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=473"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, select the Countries or Regions you want to add ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=477"
  },
  {
    "text": "custom scheduling for, and then click Next. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=479"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, choose one or more new scheduling dates ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=483"
  },
  {
    "text": "to apply to these specific Countries. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "The custom dates need to be within 48 hours ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=489"
  },
  {
    "text": "of your default selections. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=491"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this example, I've bumped my start and end date ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=493"
  },
  {
    "text": "in Europe to account for the time difference. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=495"
  },
  {
    "text": "Lock in your custom scheduling by clicking Done.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=497"
  },
  {
    "text": "And with that, you've just finished configuring ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=501"
  },
  {
    "text": "your event's availability and scheduling. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=503"
  },
  {
    "text": "There's only a few more pieces of metadata to provide. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=506"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is done in the final section ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=509"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the page, Additional Information. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=511"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, you can edit the Reference Name ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=514"
  },
  {
    "text": "that you chose earlier. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=516"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, you need to provide an Event Deep Link. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=519"
  },
  {
    "text": "This link makes it possible for users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=522"
  },
  {
    "text": "with your app installed to quickly jump ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=524"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the App Store into your In-App Event. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=526"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your event deep link can either be a universal link ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=529"
  },
  {
    "text": "or a custom URL that opens directly ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=531"
  },
  {
    "text": "to a particular place in your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=534"
  },
  {
    "text": "In order for your link to function correctly, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=536"
  },
  {
    "text": "avoid using URL shorteners or other services ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=538"
  },
  {
    "text": "that add unnecessary redirects.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=541"
  },
  {
    "text": "With the Event Purpose field, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=544"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can indicate whether your event is meant ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=546"
  },
  {
    "text": "to attract new users, keep your active users informed, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=548"
  },
  {
    "text": "or bring lapsed users back to your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=552"
  },
  {
    "text": "Many events are equally suited for all these purposes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=554"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that's the default selection. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=557"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your selection here is one of the factors ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=560"
  },
  {
    "text": "that the App Store uses to offer personalized recommendations. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=562"
  },
  {
    "text": "To help your event reach the people it's intended for, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=565"
  },
  {
    "text": "the App Store incorporates app-usage information. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=568"
  },
  {
    "text": "That data is processed on the device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=572"
  },
  {
    "text": "to minimize data collection and enhance user privacy. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=574"
  },
  {
    "text": "Note that regardless of which purpose you select, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=578"
  },
  {
    "text": "your event will be discoverable by all App Store users.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=581"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here you can indicate your event's priority level, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=585"
  },
  {
    "text": "which affects how it's ordered on your app's product page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=588"
  },
  {
    "text": "High-priority events are shown in front of normal ones, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=591"
  },
  {
    "text": "and events are sorted by their start time ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=594"
  },
  {
    "text": "within these respective groups. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=596"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, you'll indicate whether your event requires ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=598"
  },
  {
    "text": "an In-App Purchase or a Subscription.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=601"
  },
  {
    "text": "This information is displayed on your event card ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "and event details page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=607"
  },
  {
    "text": "Make sure your selection here is accurate to set ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=609"
  },
  {
    "text": "proper expectation with users and to ensure ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=611"
  },
  {
    "text": "a seamless review process.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=613"
  },
  {
    "text": "And finally, you can update your event's Primary Language. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=617"
  },
  {
    "text": "By default, this is set to your app's primary language. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=620"
  },
  {
    "text": "With that, you've now fully configured your In-App Event.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=623"
  },
  {
    "text": "Make sure you click the Save button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=628"
  },
  {
    "text": "to persist everything you just filled out.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=630"
  },
  {
    "text": "After saving, you'll notice your In-App Event ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=634"
  },
  {
    "text": "is listed in the \"draft\" state. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=636"
  },
  {
    "text": "Draft events are simply any event that you've started, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=638"
  },
  {
    "text": "but haven't yet added for review. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=641"
  },
  {
    "text": "To publish your event to the App Store, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=644"
  },
  {
    "text": "it must first be reviewed. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=646"
  },
  {
    "text": "To add your event for review, navigate back to the event page ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=648"
  },
  {
    "text": "and click the button in the top right. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=651"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll be able to add an event for review anytime ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=654"
  },
  {
    "text": "after you've filled in all the required metadata. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=656"
  },
  {
    "text": "There's no need to create a new version of your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=658"
  },
  {
    "text": "or upload a new binary. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=661"
  },
  {
    "text": "As you just saw, events begin in the draft state ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=664"
  },
  {
    "text": "and can be reviewed once fully configured.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=667"
  },
  {
    "text": "After they pass through review, events enter the approved state. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=670"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once approved, events automatically publish ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=674"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the App Store according to their scheduling. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=677"
  },
  {
    "text": "Approved events with a future publish date ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=680"
  },
  {
    "text": "are labeled \"Set to Publish,\" while those ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=682"
  },
  {
    "text": "with past publish dates are marked \"Published.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=684"
  },
  {
    "text": "After an event's end date is reached, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=689"
  },
  {
    "text": "the event moves to the \"Past\" state. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=691"
  },
  {
    "text": "While no longer published to the App Store, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=693"
  },
  {
    "text": "remember that your event details page is still ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=695"
  },
  {
    "text": "link accessible on the App Store for an additional 30 days.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=697"
  },
  {
    "text": "And finally, after 30 days in the \"Past\" state, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=702"
  },
  {
    "text": "your In-App event moves to its final state, Archived, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=705"
  },
  {
    "text": "and is no longer accessible via link.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=708"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that you understand the event state life cycle, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=712"
  },
  {
    "text": "let's discuss two important limits. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=714"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, your app can have ten events ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=717"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the approved state. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=719"
  },
  {
    "text": "And second, your app can have five events ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=721"
  },
  {
    "text": "published to the App Store at a time. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=724"
  },
  {
    "text": "You won't be able to add an event for review ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=726"
  },
  {
    "text": "if its scheduling would cause either limit to be exceeded.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=728"
  },
  {
    "text": "After your events have been published to the App Store, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=733"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's important to measure how they're performing. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=735"
  },
  {
    "text": "So there's a robust new set of capabilities ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=738"
  },
  {
    "text": "to do this in App Analytics. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=740"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your event page in App Store Connect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=742"
  },
  {
    "text": "will link directly to your event in App Analytics. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=744"
  },
  {
    "text": "From there, you'll find many important metrics ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=747"
  },
  {
    "text": "allowing you to measure your event's effectiveness.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=749"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, you'll be able to track your impressions, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=754"
  },
  {
    "text": "which shows how many people saw your event on the App Store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=757"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll also be able to drill down further, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=761"
  },
  {
    "text": "to figure out where users saw your event, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=762"
  },
  {
    "text": "like on your product page, in search, or other locations.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=764"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, you'll see metrics around how many users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=769"
  },
  {
    "text": "opened your app or opened the event details page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=772"
  },
  {
    "text": "In addition, you'll see how many users downloaded ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=776"
  },
  {
    "text": "or redownloaded your app as a result of your event. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=778"
  },
  {
    "text": "And lastly, you'll see how many users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=782"
  },
  {
    "text": "enabled notifications for your In-App Event.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=784"
  },
  {
    "text": "There's additional insights available in App Analytics ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=788"
  },
  {
    "text": "that I didn't cover, so if you're interested ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=791"
  },
  {
    "text": "in learning more, be sure to check out ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=792"
  },
  {
    "text": "the What's new in App Analytics session. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=794"
  },
  {
    "text": "And finally, we know how important it is ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=797"
  },
  {
    "text": "for you as developers to automate ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=799"
  },
  {
    "text": "as much of your app workflow process as possible. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=801"
  },
  {
    "text": "That's why I'm pleased to announce, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=804"
  },
  {
    "text": "all the In-App Event functionality I just discussed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=806"
  },
  {
    "text": "will be supported by the App Store Connect API. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=808"
  },
  {
    "text": "The full spec will be provided later this year. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=811"
  },
  {
    "text": "I've covered a lot of new information in this session. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=814"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, I showed you how users will discover ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=817"
  },
  {
    "text": "In-App Events on the App Store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=819"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, I walked you through how to set up ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=821"
  },
  {
    "text": "your In-App Events in App Store Connect. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=823"
  },
  {
    "text": "And finally, we covered how you'll be able ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=826"
  },
  {
    "text": "to measure their performance in App Analytics. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=827"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't wait to see all of the exciting events ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=830"
  },
  {
    "text": "within your apps, now discoverable on the App Store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=832"
  },
  {
    "text": "And I hope you start thinking about how you can bring ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=836"
  },
  {
    "text": "In-App Events to your own apps if you haven't already. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=838"
  },
  {
    "text": "In-App Events launch later this fall. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=841"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for watching this session, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=844"
  },
  {
    "text": "and please enjoy the rest of your conference! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=845"
  },
  {
    "text": "[upbeat music]",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10171/?time=847"
  }
